wikipedia_page.main: Thomas Murray (born 5 February 1933), known as Tom or Tommy Murray, is a Scottish former footballer who played as an inside forward in the Football League for Darlington, in the Scottish League for St Johnstone, Alloa Athletic, Albion Rovers and Stranraer, and in the Southern League for Headington United.
